## Verification checklist

- `AttackValidator`, `DefenseResolver`, `CombatEngine`, and `CombatLogBuilder` responsibilities are preserved.
- Validation runs before mutation and follows PRD order.
- Failed validation does not mutate state.
- Blocked attacks consume cards and apply only defense side effects.
- Successful attacks apply exactly the selected War card effect.
- No automatic fallback behavior exists.
- `insider` and `saboteur` behavior matches PRD.
- Defense order and side effects match PRD.
- Nal/VP clamps are applied.
- Hooks and logs follow owner-defined contracts.
- Previews are read-only.
- Blocked, failed, and successful attacks have focused GUT coverage.
